{"tid":1503562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大台出沒！民主派：撤回修訂非前設","createTime":"2019-08-25T04:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T04:49:55.000Z","uid":15828,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"431b53cd9fcc905c858fd1d3cc9e8ddf9dfe421a","tid":1503562,"uid":15828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:20:09.000Z","msg":"屌你啦死泛民！「五大訴求 缺一不可」林鄭講明如果協商係就逃犯條例撤回施壓就拒絕再談，但依家呢班粉人竟然話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">撤回唔係前設</span></span>？仲想傾？我想請大家睇下呢張圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSqrind.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSqrind.jpg&h=e66e2e5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//對於民主黨議員涂謹申提出，由政府、建制派和民主派議員三方協商，處理修訂《逃犯條例》的困局。建制派表示歡迎，但認為各方必須派出有能力決定的代表出席，否則浪費時間。<br />\n<br />\n民主派表示願意參與對話，又指撤回修例，並非對話前設。//<br />\n<br />\n記住聽埋段錄音：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457443-20190514.htm?fbclid=IwAR0nEEQk11iDxMa49JFQjyG-0R46oLqIWeMK4qtMXxLW0bl_uZpxcuPTOrg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457443-20190514.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0nEEQk11iDxMa49JFQjyG-0R46oLqIWeMK4qtMXxLW0bl_uZpxcuPTOrg&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=34ea17ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457443-20190514.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0nEEQk11iDxMa49JFQjyG-0R46oLqIWeMK4qtMXxLW0bl_uZpxcuPTOrg&h=cb49c9f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457443-20190514.htm?fbclid=IwAR0nEEQk11iDxMa49JFQjyG-0R46oLqIWeMK4qtMXxLW0bl_uZpxcuPTOrg</a><br />\n<br />\n我唔係割蓆我係防止大台出現！<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n#泛民不代表我"},{"pid":"63e8c374cbf29a45afe9a4e3af6834d602407f16","tid":1503562,"uid":15828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"572f405b7e61dd420181e884d1f2f39e7126d95d","tid":1503562,"uid":6435,"lik